		<property name="abstr"><value></value></property>
		<property name="body"><value>&lt;p&gt;Walrus is based on a single simple idea: &lt;strong&gt;the web  is writeable&lt;/strong&gt;. Like your Office document, like your touch-sensitive  iPhone, like the Sticky Note pad on your desk. Humans are used to  grabbing a pen, using their fingers, pointing and clicking with the  mouse to start writing their ideas. The Engineer believed it possible to  build complex webpages without complicated admin panels. She believed  it possible to manage content without the hassle to learn a content  management system. She coded away on the dark winter nights to put the  idea on her and her friends' screens. This is how Walrus came to be.&lt;/p&gt;</value></property>
