						<property name="body" value="&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;Time has passed. The Engineer and her friends have always been keen on   using products from the open source world, from operating systems to   databases, from servers to desktop publishing. Therefore, they have   decided that it is high time to give back to the community, to   re-release Walrus as an open source system. Getting ready for the big   day, they have crafted this demo to gather feedback and impressions. Are   you a programmer? A designer? An evangelist? Someone who just happened   to like this page? Drop us a line and share your thoughts.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;" />
